								<p>ThankSpace is a fast growing Surabaya & Denpasar based storage company that is looking for all star Field Squad Members to join our transportation team. We are looking for reliable Van Drivers, or in our words "Delivery Team" who are passionate about working with people and obsessed with delivering amazing customer service experiences.</p><p><strong>What you’ll be doing:</strong></p><p>ThankSpace will provide you with on-the-job training. You’ll be responsible for:</p><ul><li>Driving our vans throughout the Surabaya City area to drop-off and pick-up our storage bins.</li><li>Transporting items to our warehouse and assisting our warehouse team in processing or pulling items for delivery.</li><li>Actively managing our inventory levels and assisting us in preparing our bins for drop-offs.<br>Packing, wrapping, and marking oversized items according to regulation so they’re protected while in transport or at the warehouse.</li><li>&#8203;We expect a commitment of approximately 40 hours per week. Our transportation days currently run from 9am to 9pm on weekdays and weekends. You will be working out of our warehouse located in Panggung, Pabean Cantian.</li></ul><p><strong>About you:</strong></p><ul><li>Knowledge of the Surabaya area is preferred. &nbsp;</li><li>You’ve worked for a moving company, delivery company, or courier service in the past and care about properly&nbsp;</li><li>You have at least 1 year of previous commercial driving experience.</li><li>Tardiness is your pet peeve. It goes a long way if you’re dependable and punctual.</li><li>You’re a people person and love to delight others. You’ll never have a dull day in this role especially if you like making people happy.</li><li>Do you like working out? You must be able to lift heavy items (ranging from 75 to 100 lbs), sometimes in walk-up apartments. It’s a great way to stay in shape.</li><li>You love playing with technology. We’re a tech company at heart and utilize the most cutting edge technology today. You’ll help build something transformative.</li><li>You’re flexible to work weekends as needed.</li><li>A clean driving record, with no points on your license.</li><li>You are able to pass a routine drug test.</li></ul><p>
